## Build Order (Suggested Phases)

**Phase 1 — Foundation**: Project setup, Firebase config, Tailwind theme, global layout (Navbar, Footer), homepage with placeholder content. TypeScript types. Firebase helper functions.

**Phase 2 — Properties**: Property detail page with photo gallery, lightbox, amenity grid, description sections. Pull data from Firestore. Responsive layout with sticky booking widget shell.

**Phase 3 — Availability & Booking**: Availability calendar logic, date range picker, pricing calculation, booking widget fully functional. Stripe checkout integration. Booking confirmation page and email.

**Phase 4 — Admin Core**: Auth flow (login page, AuthContext, route protection). Admin layout with sidebar. Dashboard with summary stats. Bookings list and detail views.

**Phase 5 — Admin Property Management**: Photo manager (upload, reorder, delete). Property detail editor. Pricing manager with seasonal rates.

**Phase 6 — Admin Calendar & Extras**: Calendar view with color-coded bookings/blocks. Manual blocking. Reviews management. Site settings page.

**Phase 7 — Polish**: Animations (scroll reveals, page transitions). SEO metadata and structured data. Performance optimization. Mobile QA. Error handling and loading states throughout.